headline: IDEXX Laboratories to Release 2025 Second Quarter Financial Results
summary: WESTBROOK, Maine, June 24, 2025--IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. (NASDAQ: IDXX), a global leader in pet healthcare innovation, has scheduled the release of its 2025 second quarter financial results for Monday, August 4, 2025, before the market opens. The Company will conduct an analyst conference call beginning at 8:30 a.m. EDT on that day.
